data.description: WELCOME HOME TO YOUR BACKYARD OASIS! Custom built Lillian home. Sought after Midlothian ISD. SPARKLING IN GROUND POOL! Corner lot to Cul De Sac. Gorgeous tile in entryway. Gourmet kitchen with GRANITE Counters, Island and Breakfast Bar! SS Appliances. Sunlight in breakfast area overlooking your personal paradise. GORGEOUS HARDWOOD FLOORS! Open floor plan with Large living area. Classy Stone & Cozy WBFP. Spacious master bedroom with sitting area. Architectural box ceiling. Master bath has GRANITE counters. Dual sinks. Large separate shower with tile and mosaic inset. Wood floors in office with stained french doors. 3 bedrooms split from the master, all with WIC. 2nd bath is tile with classy art niche. Huge gameroom & .5 bath for entertaining upstairs. Covered patio for enjoying coffee or cookouts. Additional open patio seating in exotically landscaped backyard. Custom Well Built shed 4 storage or workshop with electricity. BONUS WORK OUT ROOM OR CRAFT ROOM. 220 in garage!
